Hold her legs.

546
00:44:40,712 --> 00:44:41,713
Look at me.

547
00:44:45,316 --> 00:44:47,552
I can handle you.

548
00:44:47,552 --> 00:44:48,353
Do it, Billy.

549
00:44:48,353 --> 00:44:50,221
Don't listen to her.

550
00:44:50,221 --> 00:44:53,658
I can see you.

551
