568
00:45:51,316 --> 00:45:53,184
Look, I'll come back for here.

569
00:45:53,184 --> 00:45:54,519
You know what, young man?

570
00:45:54,519 --> 00:45:56,021
I'm sure someday, you're gonna
make a very good sheriff,

571
